io.spine.base

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.value.ValueHolder<FieldPath>
      • io.spine.base.Field
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Immutable
public final class Field
extends ValueHolder<FieldPath>
    A reference to a Protobuf message field.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
    API Note:
    This class aggregates FieldPath for augmenting this generated class with useful methods (instead of using static utilities). This approach is used (instead of using GeneratedMixin) because Model Compiler itself depends on this package. Thus, GeneratedMixin cannot be used for augmenting generated classes that belong to it.
